<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/26647722">仅就智谋而论，历史上可以与诸葛先生比肩的甚至超过诸葛先生的都有谁？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2842132" data-action="/question/detail">

